%% PROPOSED: Flight Test Cross-Team Sequence
sequenceDiagram
    participant TL as Test Lead
    participant SW as SW Team
    participant AUTO as Autonomy
    participant HW as HW Team
    participant AERO as Aero
    participant Q as Quality
    participant FO as Field Ops
    participant PE as Project Engineer
    participant FR as WF02 FRACAS

    TL->>SW: Request software test inputs and monitoring needs
    TL->>AUTO: Request behavior objectives and success criteria
    TL->>HW: Request aircraft configuration and constraints
    TL->>AERO: Request performance objectives and data needs
    SW-->>TL: SW version and GCS support plan
    AUTO-->>TL: Behavior plan and abort triggers
    HW-->>TL: Aircraft config and readiness inputs
    AERO-->>TL: Performance metrics and analysis plan
    TL->>Q: Submit procedures and safety mitigations
    Q-->>TL: Quality review comments
    TL->>PE: Present FTRR package for readiness review
    PE->>SW: Confirm team readiness
    PE->>AUTO: Confirm team readiness
    PE->>HW: Confirm team readiness
    PE->>AERO: Confirm team readiness
    PE->>Q: Confirm safety and procedure readiness
    alt FTRR approved
        PE->>FO: Authorize test execution
        FO->>FO: Prepare aircraft and verify configuration
        FO->>TL: Aircraft ready for flight
        TL->>SW: Start real-time monitoring
        TL->>AUTO: Execute planned behaviors
        TL->>HW: Execute flight event
        par Post-flight analysis
            SW-->>TL: Logs and quick-look results
            AUTO-->>TL: Behavior analysis
            HW-->>TL: Aircraft and system inspection results
            AERO-->>TL: Performance analysis
        end
        TL->>PE: Submit flight test report
        PE-->>TL: Accept report and assign follow-up actions
        opt Issue discovered
            PE->>FR: Open corrective action in WF02
        end
    else FTRR rejected
        PE-->>TL: Rework package and reschedule review
    end
